This project is complete before adding the posting from the database. 
This project allows for the form to not be listed on the home page, but on a suburl. 
This project sucessfully writes data from the form to the database, 
However, it does not pull from the database back onto the website, yet. 
That is the next step. 
However, you could use this format to collect data, into a database, if you are not planning to post it. 
